# ------------------------
EditTag objects\weapons\rifle\plasma_repeater\fx\firing.effect
SetField Events[0].Parts[0].Type dw3\r3ach\sound\weapons\plasma_repeater\plas_repeater_fire.sound
SetField Events[0].Parts[1].Type dw3\r3ach\sound\weapons\plasma_repeater\plas_repeater_lod_far.sound
SaveTagChanges
Exit

EditTag objects\weapons\rifle\plasma_repeater\fx\venting.effect
