SetField Events[0].ParticleSystems[1].Emitters[0].RuntimeMGpu.UsedParticleStates Age,SystemAge,Random4,SystemLod,Random6,Random7,Random8,SystemRandom3
SetField Events[0].ParticleSystems[1].Emitters[0].RuntimeMGpu.Properties[1].MInnardsW.FBitfield 131072

